# Finess

## Info
###### Artline__ (Me)

[Website](http://www.officialartline.com/)
[Twitter](https://twitter.com/Artline__)

===

[Brackets version (Coming soon..)]()

Current version: 1.0.0 - [Changelog](https://github.com/OfficialArtline/atom-finess-syntax/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md)

## Installation
1. Go to Settings > Install > Themes(Press the Themes button) > Search for "finess" > Press "Install"
2. Go to Settings > Themes > Change "Syntax Theme" to "Finess"
